            (X.1 ‚óÅ (Y.1 ‚óÅ f ‚â´ (HalfBraiding.Œ≤ Y.2 U').hom)) ‚äó‚â´
              (HalfBraiding.Œ≤ X.2 U').hom ‚ñ∑ Y.1 ‚äó‚â´ ùüô _ := by coherence
