            X.1 ‚óÅ (HalfBraiding.Œ≤ Y.2 U).hom ‚äó‚â´
              (X.1 ‚óÅ f ‚â´ (HalfBraiding.Œ≤ X.2 U').hom) ‚ñ∑ Y.1 ‚äó‚â´ ùüô _ := by
            rw [HalfBraiding.naturality]; coherence
